{"tid":2101831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"哈薩克稱「哈肺炎」是假新聞","createTime":"2020-07-10T05:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T02:26:41.000Z","uid":348984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bd0b7fee53b59497cb1a426bd7cccfccffffe5","tid":2101831,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"中國提醒在哈薩克的中國公民注意防範比武漢肺炎更致命的「哈肺炎」，哈薩克當局直指是假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐哈薩克大使館昨日發布公告說，哈薩克今年不明原因肺炎，上半年已導致 1772 人死亡，其中 628 人是在六月殆命。中國大使館將這個「疾病」稱為「哈肺炎」，指比現時被俗稱為「武漢肺炎」的 2019 冠狀病毒病致死率更高。<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克衛生部回應直指中國散布的是假新聞，稱這些病例是在臨床上出現了武漢肺炎的病徵，但未被正式確診的個案。哈薩克強調一直有對此類個案作監測，以及時作出疫情應對。"},{"pid":"46ec3be3fa4e4036e7754f5594533753cfc13e54","tid":2101831,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"支那狗得返中東 東亞班fd都要得罪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正一弱智仔黎"},{"pid":"577fb96ec13cb5904a9562178c2d792a305561ad","tid":2101831,"uid":15592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"話人地叫武漢肺炎係歧視，自己又用人地國家名去改隻假病名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be238f2c907c374502824e2386971b5fa6f51caa","tid":2101831,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"中共統治下 有咩係真？ 大家都明啦"},{"pid":"7396be66b63393850c7228b45ca762da43e79439","tid":2101831,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:13:40.000Z","msg":"Of course, it&rsquo;s fake. It&rsquo;s WuHan virus to begin with. Lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdd79a8639378b23c533e91539f340412ac1538","tid":2101831,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"上次先屈完人想回歸強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9079e06eebcdc0f0fc4ee01ae11328fd4799aff4","ti